headline: Leidos Announces Agreement to Sell Varec
summary: Leidos (NYSE: LDOS) has entered into a definitive agreement to sell its wholly owned subsidiary, Varec. The transaction is in support of portfolio optimization efforts under its NorthStar 2030 strategy unveiled earlier this year.
